- (YAMI4Parameters *) getNestedParameters

Extracts the nested parameters value from the current entry.

Extracts the nested parameters value from the current entry.

Returns:
Pointer to the proxy object that represents the internally stored parameters object. The returned value is newly allocated and has to be managed by caller; note that releasing it does not remove the represented entry.
